    "body" : "<p>just use <strong><a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/6/docs/api/java/io/File.html#getName%28%29\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">File.getName()</a></strong></p>\n<pre><code>File f = new File(&quot;C:\\\\Hello\\\\AnotherFolder\\\\The File Name.PDF&quot;);\nSystem.out.println(f.getName());\n</code></pre>\n<p>using <strong>String methods</strong>:</p>\n<pre><code>  File f = new File(&quot;C:\\\\Hello\\\\AnotherFolder\\\\The File Name.PDF&quot;);  \nSystem.out.println(f.getAbsolutePath().substring(f.getAbsolutePath().lastIndexOf(File.separator)+1));\n</code></pre>\n"
