    "body" : "<p>Alternative using <a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/nio/file/Path.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><code>Path</code></a> (Java 7+):</p>\n\n<pre><code>Path p = Paths.get(\"C:\\\\Hello\\\\AnotherFolder\\\\The File Name.PDF\");\nString file = p.getFileName().toString();\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Note that splitting the string on <code>\\\\</code> is platform dependent as the file separator might vary. <code>Path#getName</code> takes care of that issue for you.</p>\n"
